ğŸŒ¿ Garden Tips
Trending
GET /trending/tips
â†’ Fetch the most popular garden tips based on likes, comments, or views.

CRUD Operations
GET /api/garden-tips
â†’ Retrieve all garden tips from the database.

POST /api/garden-tips (Protected)
â†’ Create a new garden tip. Requires authentication.

GET /api/garden-tips/:id
â†’ Get a specific garden tip by its ID.

PUT /api/garden-tips/:id (Protected: Author/Admin)
â†’ Update an existing garden tip.

DELETE /api/garden-tips/:id (Protected: Author/Admin)
â†’ Delete a specific garden tip.

ğŸ” Authentication
